{
  "stem": "268.8",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I'll be working with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so I put down my name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I even got ration cards in German, which were a blessing then, but which almost turn out to be my downfall after liberation.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I get to that in a minute.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "With those people I spend, and I got to like it very much.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was a whole family, the Belarusians-- like a patriarch-- a grandfather, with two sons, a daughter, son-in-laws, cousin.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he was sort of the patriarch of the family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In the evenings, he would sit down, tell stories, talk about the Russia and all that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But the last few evenings, when the front was beginning to near, he was talking in a whisper to the rest of your family members.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He's afraid of the Russians advancing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they kept saying, no, the Americans are coming because he didn't want to be liberated by the Russian troops because of his anti-Russian sentiments.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he was afraid he'd be sent to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I forget the name-- the date in May-- must've been 3rd, 4th, or something like that, the town's police chief already left.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the SS, the police were already run away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that evening, they got together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He kept talking in Russian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He says, we have to run away because I heard that the Russians are coming to our town.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "On the other side of the Albania, Americans already there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the Russians came that night, before he could run away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was going to go with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were going to take me with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Russian liberated us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I'd like to tell you a small detail, which is very important, also-- again, another little miracle.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this was a miracle at liberation.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
